{"tid":1465360,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【即時戰術·置頂】唔好問點解住，我地要做好準備先。","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:24.000Z","uid":136008,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2353144c74c9ec45d34898034a005324b9a9af46","tid":1465360,"uid":136008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"依家唔係賽後檢討嘅狀態。<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩分唔分化住，都唔好問對方點解唔走，點解要走，全部人應該留意事態（機場）<br />\n<br />\n無論你理解成圍魏救趙又好，定係一方有難八方支援都好，我地如果睇到機場有大量警力或者有即時嘅行動，每一區就應該做返我地應該做嘅嘢。<br />\n對面警力有限一定會亂。<br />\n<br />\n記住啦！不分化，不割蓆！<br />\nBe water 全部人保持冷靜 要做就一齊做，一齊支援。<br />\n全部都係兄弟！"},{"pid":"540f705631ddfdbcf69c2ad2bdc8572e1d01c84f","tid":1465360,"uid":136008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"全世界都要知"},{"pid":"2d3d16cf563915643eb88a1d799cd62f1ad677cb","tid":1465360,"uid":136008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"全世界都要知"},{"pid":"28325395c92b122374127ab39d53e882627283ee","tid":1465360,"uid":136008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"全世界都要知"},{"pid":"070b2058d987f0fac2aecd4b71d899db4e841891","tid":1465360,"uid":136008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"全世界都要知"},{"pid":"65a3467f2f1e677a0bcf912feb1240be8fa9304c","tid":1465360,"uid":151608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n要幫手足分擔"},{"pid":"06cd62b3e9de3ea056b594da79d5411a99162aaf","tid":1465360,"uid":136008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"全世界都要知，記住啦 係機場一有大事件發生我地就要即刻做嘢，保持冷靜 唔好輕舉妄動"},{"pid":"b0684829c008906911de5864a359cb18599e63c6","tid":1465360,"uid":151608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f2604114db07f692c2d596464c3a09d75163f1e","tid":1465360,"uid":151608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0